## Code quality rules

- No `any` — use typed fixtures and proper generics
- No unicode bullet characters (`•`) in text — these are display concerns, not test concerns
- Keep each test file focused on one module
- `beforeEach` to reset mocks; `afterEach` for `vi.useRealTimers()` if fake timers are used
- Always call `vi.clearAllMocks()` or `mockReset()` in `beforeEach`
